@{
    ViewBag.Title = "About Us";
}
<h2>@ViewBag.Title.</h2>
<h3>@ViewBag.Message</h3>

<p>
    HealthPro is an application that allows its users to manage their weight by keeping a track on their calorie intake. This is a Health and Nutrition monitoring website constructed in ASP.NET MVC C# application. Some of the goals of this application will be:
    <br /><br />
    •	Keep track of user’s weight and body mass index to determine if they are healthy<br />
    •	Set healthy goals and work toward meeting them<br />
    •	Use calorie counter to maintain a healthy diet plan<br />
    •	Lose or gain weight by tracking his calorie intake<br />
    <br /><br />
    This application will have a master/ home page, about us, contact us, food, my goals, register and login. The home page will provide navigation through entire website. About us and contact us pages will have some detail on how we work and what we want to achieve. The food page will have a search option for user to browse through a variety of foods and find their calorie count. It will give information on nutrient foods such as foods with high potassium, iron, calcium and carbohydrates. My goals page will allow user to enter a starting weight, a goal weight, his weekly goal i.e. how much weight he wants to gain or lose in a week.
</p>
